<lb n="0225b22" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0225b23" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225b24" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 1248</head>
<lb n="0225b25" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0225002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】享和元年刊長谷寺藏本，【甲】高山寺藏古寫本</note><jhead>北方毘沙門天王隨軍護法真言</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0225b26" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225b27" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門
<lb n="0225b28" ed="T"/>大廣智不空別行翻譯不入正經</byline>
<lb n="0225b29" ed="T"/><div1 type="dharani"><p id="pT21p0225b2901" type="dharani"><note n="0225003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此梵字真言附載於卷末</note>曩謨囉多曩<note place="inline">二合</note>多羅<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0225004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔多〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0225004" resp="【原】" corr="＆lac；">多</sic>夜耶阿馱佉路
<pb n="0225c" id="T21.1248.0225c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0225c01" ed="T"/>步多囉<note place="inline">二合</note>耶地舍耶<note place="inline">二</note>吠室囉<note place="inline">二合</note>摩拏野<note place="inline">三</note>
<lb n="0225c02" ed="T"/>摩賀囉惹野<note place="inline">四</note>藥迦灑<note place="inline">二合</note>地婆多婆<note place="inline">五上</note>娑都
<lb n="0225c03" ed="T"/>哆娑娑室囉跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>娑賀娜耶呬<note place="inline">賢二反</note>摩馱吒
<lb n="0225c04" ed="T"/>吒<note place="inline">去<note n="0225005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">呼＝乎【甲】</note><app n="0225005"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">乎</rdg></app></note>尾跛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>灑夜迷跛娜也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note n="0225006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">保＝俁【甲】＊</note><app n="0225006"><lem wit="【大】">保</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俁</rdg></app>
<lb n="0225c05" ed="T"/>&CB04048;&CB00135;<app source="0225006" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">保</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">俁</rdg></app>&CB04048;&CB00135;俱沙吠室羅摩拏野摩賀囉惹
<lb n="0225c06" ed="T"/>耶綺<note place="inline">佉罽反</note>婆<note place="inline">去</note>馱伽&CB00135;多囉摩熾都麼麼<note place="inline">某甲受持</note>捺
<lb n="0225c07" ed="T"/>娑<note place="inline">上</note>娑馱耶娑那謨婆&CB00344;&CB00085;帝悉殿都麼多囉
<lb n="0225c08" ed="T"/>跛馱&CB00135;娑婆<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</p>
<lb n="0225c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0225c0901">若行者受持此&CB00057;者。先須畫像。於彩色中並
<lb n="0225c10" ed="T"/>不得和膠。於白&CB00626;上畫一毘沙門神。七寶莊
<lb n="0225c11" ed="T"/>嚴衣甲。左手執戟&CB00266;。右手<note n="0225007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">托＝託【甲】</note><app n="0225007"><lem wit="【大】">托</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">託</rdg></app>腰上。其神&CB00560;
<lb n="0225c12" ed="T"/>下作二夜叉鬼。身並作黑色。其毘沙門面。作
<lb n="0225c13" ed="T"/>甚可畏形惡眼視一切鬼神勢。其塔奉釋迦
<lb n="0225c14" ed="T"/>牟尼佛。教汝若領天兵守界擁護國土。何護
<lb n="0225c15" ed="T"/>吾法。即擁遣第三子那吒捧行莫離其側。汝
<lb n="0225c16" ed="T"/>眼毒惡恐損眾生。爾時行者。若誦此&CB00057;時。就
<lb n="0225c17" ed="T"/>好地。勿使有穢惡之處。極令淨潔取牛糞塗
<lb n="0225c18" ed="T"/>地。即以香泥塗之。散種種花燒香供養。行者
<lb n="0225c19" ed="T"/>上下衣服。並須清淨一上廁一洗浴。白月十
<lb n="0225c20" ed="T"/>五日夜。起首對像前。誦&CB00057;滿十萬遍訖。然
<lb n="0225c21" ed="T"/>後更取香泥復塗壇上。更取上妙好花散壇
<lb n="0225c22" ed="T"/>中。設種種飲食。行者取薰陸香一百八顆。各
<lb n="0225c23" ed="T"/>&CB00057;一遍散著火中。爾時毘沙門即現其身。行
<lb n="0225c24" ed="T"/>者若見神時取上好食飲。供養毘沙門神通。
<lb n="0225c25" ed="T"/>行者心中所願其神悉見。若行者不見神時。
<lb n="0225c26" ed="T"/>即虛空中有聲<note n="0225008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">云＝告言&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225008"><lem wit="【大】">云</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">告言</rdg></app>。汝但<note n="0225009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝懃&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225009"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">懃</rdg></app>心<note n="0225010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">持誦＝誦&CB00057;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225010"><lem wit="【大】">持誦</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">誦&CB00057;</rdg></app>。一切
<lb n="0225c27" ed="T"/>事汝欲者悉如意。若不見神及不聞聲。但有
<lb n="0225c28" ed="T"/>大風。或雲遍滿布其壇上。其法即成就。若
<lb n="0225c29" ed="T"/>無上件等相。<note n="0225011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">行者＝更&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225011"><lem wit="【大】">行者</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">更</rdg></app>誦&CB00057;<note n="0225012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）&M062403;＋七【原】</note><app n="0225012"><lem wit="【大】">七</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">一七</rdg></app>遍。縛得<note n="0225013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">入＝人&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0225013"><lem wit="【大】">入</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">人</rdg></app>者
<pb n="0226a" id="T21.1248.0226a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0226a01" ed="T"/>其法即成。更勿懷疑。</p><p id="pT21p0226a0109" place="inline">又法若行者欲得喝
<lb n="0226a02" ed="T"/>囉闍愛敬者。取赤小豆一顆&CB00057;一遍。投火中
<lb n="0226a03" ed="T"/>燒。如是滿一百八遍。其喝囉闍即遣人<note n="0226001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喚來極忽＝喚&CB00057;師如箭急急來&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226001"><lem wit="【大】">喚
<lb n="0226a04" ed="T"/>來極忽</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">喚&CB00057;師如箭急急來</rdg></app>。</p><p id="pT21p0226a0404" place="inline">又法若欲得大<note n="0226002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">官＝印【甲】</note><app n="0226002"><lem wit="【大】">官</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">印</rdg></app>人愛敬者。取
<lb n="0226a05" ed="T"/><note n="0226003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔白〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226003"><lem wit="【大】">白</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>芥子一顆。一&CB00057;投火中燒滿一百八遍。其
<lb n="0226a06" ed="T"/>官即自<note n="0226004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔來〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226004"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>敬仰大喜。</p><p id="pT21p0226a0609" place="inline">又法於白月十五日
<lb n="0226a07" ed="T"/>作壇。於像前作八肘。牛糞塗地了。取香泥
<lb n="0226a08" ed="T"/>重塗了。以五色畫作三重院。其壇內於中畫
<lb n="0226a09" ed="T"/>一<note n="0226005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝火&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226005"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">火</rdg></app>輪。四角拔折羅十字安之。第二院內。
<lb n="0226a10" ed="T"/>東面畫作一火珠光焰<note n="0226006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝上&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226006"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">上</rdg></app>出。南面畫三<note n="0226007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝鈷【甲】</note><app n="0226007"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">鈷</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0226a11" ed="T"/>又西面畫一龍口中<note n="0226008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">並＝著&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226008"><lem wit="【大】">並</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">著</rdg></app>出蓮華。北面畫一大
<lb n="0226a12" ed="T"/><note n="0226009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縲＝螺&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226009"><lem wit="【大】">縲</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">螺</rdg></app>。第三院中東面<note n="0226010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔更〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226010"><lem wit="【大】">更</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>畫師子。南面畫龍
<lb n="0226a13" ed="T"/>王。西面畫孔雀王<note n="0226011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔鳥〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226011"><lem wit="【大】">鳥</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>。北面畫<note n="0226012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅剎手＝夜叉王&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226012"><lem wit="【大】">羅剎手</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">夜叉王</rdg></app>拄<note n="0226013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">棒＝杖&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226013"><lem wit="【大】">棒</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">杖</rdg></app>
<lb n="0226a14" ed="T"/>立地。壇四角各安香水瓶。內著雜&CB00031;楊枝。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226a15" ed="T"/>師洗浴著新淨衣。於像前設種種飲食供養。
<lb n="0226a16" ed="T"/>即誦&CB00057;取呵梨勒<note n="0226014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">一顆＝一百八顆&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226014"><lem wit="【大】">一顆</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">一百八顆</rdg></app>。一&CB00057;一遍投火中燒
<lb n="0226a17" ed="T"/>之。滿一百八遍。從今已後。每日送一<note n="0226015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB04123;＝送金一鋋&M062403;【原】，鎰&M062485;【原】</note><note n="0226015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB04123;＝送金一鋋&M062403;【原】，＝鎰&M062485;【原】</note><app n="0226015"><lem wit="【大】"><sic resp="【原】" corr="鎰">&CB04123;</sic></lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">送金一鋋</rdg></app>金
<lb n="0226a18" ed="T"/>與&CB00057;師永無乏少。若得此物即須用盡。不得
<lb n="0226a19" ed="T"/>留著。</p><p id="pT21p0226a1903" place="inline">又法&CB00057;蘇蜜及&CB00031;子。一百八遍火中
<lb n="0226a20" ed="T"/>燒之。一切諸天皆大歡喜擁護&CB00057;師。</p><p id="pT21p0226a2015" place="inline">又法
<lb n="0226a21" ed="T"/>若欲遠行時。&CB00057;穀木<note n="0226016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">柱＝拄杖&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226016"><lem wit="【大】">柱</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">拄杖</rdg></app>行一切難處。悉得
<lb n="0226a22" ed="T"/>無怖。又法若惡人相惱亂者。心中想此&CB00057;
<lb n="0226a23" ed="T"/>神形。復舉心誦&CB00057;。未滿一遍。其人即不能
<lb n="0226a24" ed="T"/><note n="0226017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（行）&M062403;＋動【原】</note><app n="0226017"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">行動</rdg></app>。</p><p id="pT21p0226a2402" place="inline">若欲好者。心放中相<note n="0226018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＋（云即）【甲】</note><app n="0226018"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">便云即</rdg></app>得解脫。</p><p id="pT21p0226a2414" place="inline">又
<lb n="0226a25" ed="T"/>法若欲令怨家<note n="0226019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不同住＝遠相&CB00230;&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226019"><lem wit="【大】">不同住</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">遠相&CB00230;</rdg></app>者。取苦練<note n="0226020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝木&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226020"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">木</rdg></app>一百
<lb n="0226a26" ed="T"/>八顆。一&CB00057;<note n="0226021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（一）＋投【甲】</note><app n="0226021"><lem wit="【大】">投</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">一投</rdg></app>火中。其人即自遠去。</p><p id="pT21p0226a2614" place="inline">又法
<lb n="0226a27" ed="T"/>若&CB00057;胡麻一百八遍。散著火中。一切人盡來
<lb n="0226a28" ed="T"/>供養&CB00057;師。</p><p id="pT21p0226a2805" place="inline">又法若&CB00057;白芥子一百八遍散山
<lb n="0226a29" ed="T"/>中。一切惡獸不能傷人。其<note n="0226022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狩＝獸&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0226022" resp="【原】" corr="獸">狩</sic>見人即自伏
<pb n="0226b" id="T21.1248.0226b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0226b01" ed="T"/>地不敢傷害。過去已後方即起去。</p><p id="pT21p0226b0114" place="inline">又法若
<lb n="0226b02" ed="T"/>欲乞雨時。<note n="0226023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔取〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226023"><lem wit="【大】">取</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>杏<note n="0226024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＋（人）【原】</note><app n="0226024"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】">子人</rdg></app>一百八顆都&CB00057;三七遍。
<lb n="0226b03" ed="T"/>著有龍水中必得雨下。欲止雨時。取梧桐子
<lb n="0226b04" ed="T"/>火中燒之即止。</p><p id="pT21p0226b0407" place="inline">又法若行者欲乞食。先&CB00057;
<lb n="0226b05" ed="T"/>&CB00425;一百八遍。隨所<note n="0226025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">到＝致【甲】</note><app n="0226025"><lem wit="【大】">到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">致</rdg></app>處。自然而得一切飲
<lb n="0226b06" ed="T"/>食了。飲<note n="0226026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔食〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226026"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>殘者當時自化<note n="0226027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">去＝土【甲】</note><app n="0226027"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">土</rdg></app>。若須飲食時。
<lb n="0226b07" ed="T"/>至心向&CB00425;<note n="0226028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226028"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>誦&CB00057;一遍。其&CB00425;依還如故。</p><p id="pT21p0226b0716" place="inline">又
<lb n="0226b08" ed="T"/>法若欲見功<note n="0226029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">能＝德【甲】＊</note><app n="0226029"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">德</rdg></app>天者。一日一夜不食。於佛
<lb n="0226b09" ed="T"/>前燒蘇合香。&CB00057;白花一百八遍。以散<note n="0226030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">神＝佛&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226030"><lem wit="【大】">神</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">佛</rdg></app>前。
<lb n="0226b10" ed="T"/>其功<app source="0226029" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">能</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">德</rdg></app>天即自現身。隨意所須一切願滿。所
<lb n="0226b11" ed="T"/>求財寶即得稱意。</p><p id="pT21p0226b1108" place="inline">若欲<note n="0226031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辟＝避&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226031"><lem wit="【大】">辟</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">避</rdg></app>除一切鬼神。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226b12" ed="T"/>白芥子及蘇。&CB00057;一顆一遍。投火中燒之即得。</p>
<lb n="0226b13" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0226b1301">若有<note n="0226032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">官＝惡&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226032"><lem wit="【大】">官</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">惡</rdg></app>人。於三寶<note n="0226033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">中＝所&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226033"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">所</rdg></app>起不善心者。惱亂
<lb n="0226b14" ed="T"/>佛弟子者。欲令起慈心。須作降伏。&CB00057;手<note n="0226034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">三＝二&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226034"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">二</rdg></app>
<lb n="0226b15" ed="T"/>十一遍。遙打之其人即著疾。欲<note n="0226035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">好＝改&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226035"><lem wit="【大】">好</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">改</rdg></app>者慈心
<lb n="0226b16" ed="T"/>誦一遍即差。</p><p id="pT21p0226b1606" place="inline">又法&CB00057;土二十一遍。散自身
<lb n="0226b17" ed="T"/>上。一切人<note n="0226036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＋（者）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226036"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">見者</rdg></app>無不敬仰。欲令自身有威光
<lb n="0226b18" ed="T"/>者。&CB00057;墨塗額上。一切人見者無不愛仰。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226b19" ed="T"/>灰二十一遍。塗其身大眾中一切人<note n="0226037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">見＝者【甲】</note><app n="0226037"><lem wit="【大】">見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">者</rdg></app>皆福
<lb n="0226b20" ed="T"/>德相。眾人供養。欲得遠涉道路不被惡人
<lb n="0226b21" ed="T"/>惡<note n="0226038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狩＝獸&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226038"><lem wit="【大】">狩</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">獸</rdg></app>傷害。行<note n="0226039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">加＝如&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0226039" resp="【原】" corr="如">加</sic>奔馬。&CB00057;左<note n="0226040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">手＋（以四指握）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226040"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">手以四指握</rdg></app>大母指作
<lb n="0226b22" ed="T"/><note n="0226041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝拳&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226041"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">拳</rdg></app>。而去欲得於鏡看事。&CB00057;童<note n="0226042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝男&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226042"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">男</rdg></app>童女問吉
<lb n="0226b23" ed="T"/>凶。其人即自下語。令道所病鬼姓名。即知
<lb n="0226b24" ed="T"/>是何等之病。</p><p id="pT21p0226b2406" place="inline">若被<note n="0226043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">蠱＝蟲&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226043"><lem wit="【大】">蠱</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">蟲</rdg></app>毒食者。&CB00057;所食物二
<lb n="0226b25" ed="T"/>十一遍。其所為毒即吐出。</p><p id="pT21p0226b2511" place="inline">若患鬼病&CB00057;五
<lb n="0226b26" ed="T"/>色線。一遍一結一百八遍了。繫頭上或頂上
<lb n="0226b27" ed="T"/>臂上。一切病患除差。</p><p id="pT21p0226b2709" place="inline">若患心<note n="0226044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝痛&M062403;【原】＊</note><app n="0226044"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">痛</rdg></app>。&CB00057;石榴
<lb n="0226b28" ed="T"/><note n="0226045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔花〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226045"><lem wit="【大】">花</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>汁飲之即愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226b2807" place="inline">若欲攝<note n="0226046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">狐魅＝野狐&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226046"><lem wit="【大】">狐魅</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">野狐</rdg></app>病。&CB00057;五色
<lb n="0226b29" ed="T"/>線。令童<note n="0226047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">子＝女&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226047"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">女</rdg></app>合<note n="0226048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔成〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226048"><lem wit="【大】">成</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>索。一&CB00057;一結一百八遍。繫
<pb n="0226c" id="T21.1248.0226c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0226c01" ed="T"/><note n="0226049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">項＝頸【甲】</note><app n="0226049"><lem wit="【大】">項</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頸</rdg></app>下。<note n="0226050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">復＝更&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226050"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">更</rdg></app>&CB00057;楊枝打病者即立愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0113" place="inline">若患骨
<lb n="0226c02" ed="T"/>節<note n="0226051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔楚〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226051"><lem wit="【大】">楚</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>病。&CB00057;<note n="0226052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宥＝鎖鐵&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226052"><lem wit="【大】">宥</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">鎖鐵</rdg></app>刀禁其病即愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0212" place="inline">若欲護身。
<lb n="0226c03" ed="T"/>&CB00057;白芥子二十一遍。若灰若水亦然。散四方
<lb n="0226c04" ed="T"/>為界。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0403" place="inline">若頭<app source="0226044" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">痛</rdg></app>或身病&CB00057;蘇烏麻油二十一
<lb n="0226c05" ed="T"/>遍。摩塗其身即愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0508" place="inline">若患耳風&CB00057;蘇二十一
<lb n="0226c06" ed="T"/>遍食之愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0605" place="inline">若患眼。&CB00057;杏人油塗之立愈。</p>
<lb n="0226c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0226c0701">若患腫。&CB00057;石榴<note n="0226053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">黃＝及黃檀香&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226053"><lem wit="【大】">黃</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">及黃檀香</rdg></app>一百八遍塗上即愈。或白
<lb n="0226c08" ed="T"/>檀香亦得。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0805" place="inline">若患頭<note n="0226054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">病＝頂&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226054"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">頂</rdg></app>。&CB00057;大黃二十一遍。塗
<lb n="0226c09" ed="T"/>額上即愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c0905" place="inline">若患時氣病。&CB00057;青木香末二十
<lb n="0226c10" ed="T"/>一遍。和水服之立愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1009" place="inline">若患惡瘡疥癬者。取
<lb n="0226c11" ed="T"/>利蘆<note n="0226055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝末&M062403;【原】，木【甲】</note><note n="0226055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未＝末&M062403;【原】，＝木【甲】</note><app n="0226055"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">末</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">木</rdg></app>和油塗上立即除愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1112" place="inline">若患瘧病。&CB00057;
<lb n="0226c12" ed="T"/>楊枝二十一遍<note n="0226056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令打病人＝令病人把【甲】</note><app n="0226056"><lem wit="【大】">令打病人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">令病人把</rdg></app>即時除愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1215" place="inline">若被
<lb n="0226c13" ed="T"/>蝎<note n="0226057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">螫＝赦【甲】</note><app n="0226057"><lem wit="【大】">螫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">赦</rdg></app>。&CB00057;乾脯火中<note n="0226058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燒之熱＝熱燒&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226058"><lem wit="【大】">燒之。熱</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">熱燒</rdg></app>拄其上便即除
<lb n="0226c14" ed="T"/>愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1402" place="inline">若被蛇咬。&CB00057;畢<note n="0226059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00425;＝撥枝&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226059"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00425;</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">撥枝</rdg></app>二十一遍。塗之當下
<lb n="0226c15" ed="T"/>即愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1503" place="inline">若婦人乳腫。&CB00057;油麻嚼塗上即差。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1516" place="inline">若
<lb n="0226c16" ed="T"/>帶下病者。&CB00057;<note n="0226060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔丁〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0226060"><lem wit="【大】">丁</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>香水服之<note n="0226061" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔即愈〕－【甲】</note><app n="0226061"><lem wit="【大】">即愈</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1613" place="inline">若人卒
<lb n="0226c17" ed="T"/>被鬼著狂言荒語。&CB00057;水<note n="0226062" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝含&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226062"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">含</rdg></app><note n="0226063" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">服之＝其服&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226063"><lem wit="【大】">服之</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">其服</rdg></app>。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1713" place="inline">若患心
<lb n="0226c18" ed="T"/><app source="0226044" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">痛</rdg></app>。&CB00057;黃土塗之。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1807" place="inline">若患一切鬼<note n="0226064" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">魅＋（病）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0226064"><lem wit="【大】">魅</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">魅病</rdg></app>者。&CB00057;石
<lb n="0226c19" ed="T"/>榴枝一百八遍。用打病者即愈。</p><p id="pT21p0226c1913" place="inline">若欲得成
<lb n="0226c20" ed="T"/>就三事者。當於像前作壇。壇內散種種名花。
<pb n="0227a" id="T21.1248.0227a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0227a01" ed="T"/>設種種飲食訖。取赤銅&CB04122;一枚。雄黃三兩細
<lb n="0227a02" ed="T"/>擣和蜜水為丸置像前。取荷葉覆上。以手掩
<lb n="0227a03" ed="T"/>之&CB00057;不息。當有相現。若&CB00195;出時取塗身上。即
<lb n="0227a04" ed="T"/>成安怛陀那。若火出時。手取火焰用塗面上。
<lb n="0227a05" ed="T"/>一切眾生見此人者皆大歡喜敬仰有大威
<lb n="0227a06" ed="T"/>光。所出言教人皆信受恭敬隨順。若有煖氣
<lb n="0227a07" ed="T"/>其人即取塗身即得無盡。</p><p id="pT21p0227a0711" place="inline">又法於舍利塔前
<lb n="0227a08" ed="T"/>&CB00057;牛黃。依前藥法皆得塗身一切福德盡集
<lb n="0227a09" ed="T"/>其身。所在眾生見如羅闍無異。</p><p id="pT21p0227a0913" place="inline">又法<note n="0227001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">若＋（欲）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227001"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">若欲</rdg></app>知
<lb n="0227a10" ed="T"/>山間有孔似阿修羅窟者。當&CB00057;白芥子和自
<lb n="0227a11" ed="T"/>身血。一&CB00057;一遍打山間孔。盡一千八遍。其山
<lb n="0227a12" ed="T"/>窟自開。其阿修羅女身如火然。持諸香花<note n="0227002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">迎＝及&M062403;【原】，取【甲】</note><note n="0227002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迎＝及&M062403;【原】，＝取【甲】</note><app n="0227002"><lem wit="【大】">迎</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">及</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">取</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227a13" ed="T"/>&CB00057;師來。行者入此窟內。壽命一大劫身力還
<lb n="0227a14" ed="T"/>如阿修羅。亦如金剛無能損者。若欲出時亦
<lb n="0227a15" ed="T"/>得一切阿修羅女隨從。若不還時亦到<note n="0227003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">火＝大【甲】</note><app n="0227003"><lem wit="【大】">火</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">大</rdg></app>終
<lb n="0227a16" ed="T"/>無所害。</p><p id="pT21p0227a1604" place="inline">又法將此像向舍利塔前。香塗地
<lb n="0227a17" ed="T"/>香花散於壇內。上妙供養了。取梨木作合子。
<lb n="0227a18" ed="T"/>取安膳那石為末。用秦膠水為丸。盛於合子
<lb n="0227a19" ed="T"/>中置壇中。行者著新淨衣。在於像前一日不
<lb n="0227a20" ed="T"/>食。誦此&CB00057;一千八遍<note n="0227004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">了＝竟&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227004"><lem wit="【大】">了</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">竟</rdg></app>。亦無勞三相現。&CB00057;
<lb n="0227a21" ed="T"/>一千八遍訖<note n="0227005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">塗＝用【甲】</note><app n="0227005"><lem wit="【大】">塗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">用</rdg></app>眼竟。<note n="0227006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">即＝亦&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227006"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">亦</rdg></app>塗&CB00560;<note n="0227007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">掌＝常【甲】</note><app n="0227007"><lem wit="【大】">掌</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">常</rdg></app>心中胸前
<lb n="0227a22" ed="T"/>兩膊上<note n="0227008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔頂〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227008"><lem wit="【大】">頂</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>竟。至心合掌思身如虛空。無有
<lb n="0227a23" ed="T"/>身相作<note n="0227009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自＝此&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227009"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">此</rdg></app>想時。行者隱形日行千里。一切事
<lb n="0227a24" ed="T"/>業&CB00278;皆悉見。</p><p id="pT21p0227a2406" place="inline">又法欲得伏外道入火中。取自
<lb n="0227a25" ed="T"/>身血魚血。瞋心誦此&CB00057;二十一遍。投火中即
<lb n="0227a26" ed="T"/>入火中。<note n="0227010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">得一頃食＝經一食頃&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227010"><lem wit="【大】">得一頃食</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">經一食頃</rdg></app>間不燒其身。</p><p id="pT21p0227a2613" place="inline">又法若欲
<lb n="0227a27" ed="T"/>降伏外道。手中結印。瞋心誦&CB00057;一百八遍。外
<lb n="0227a28" ed="T"/>道所作法悉破壞&CB00278;不成就。</p><p id="pT21p0227a2812" place="inline">又法若欲降伏
<lb n="0227a29" ed="T"/>諸國兵賊眾者。當畫一像身卦紫磨真金甲。
<pb n="0227b" id="T21.1248.0227b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0227b01" ed="T"/>於淨室中燒眾名香乳頭薰陸香。諸色香花
<lb n="0227b02" ed="T"/>飲食供養。<note n="0227011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">真＝瞋&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227011"><lem wit="【大】">真</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">瞋</rdg></app>心誦念天王真言十萬遍。天王
<lb n="0227b03" ed="T"/>領天兵來助。他國兵敵自退散。若能晝夜誦
<lb n="0227b04" ed="T"/>念不絕。天王使太子獨健。領天兵千人衛護
<lb n="0227b05" ed="T"/>不離其側。所求如意應念隨心。皆得成就。</p>
<lb n="0227b06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0227b0601">又法若欲降前敵眾者。於淨室持齋畫一天
<lb n="0227b07" ed="T"/>王形像。卦紫磨真金甲。於二丈竿懸。軍前五
<lb n="0227b08" ed="T"/>十步指其敵。其敵不能相患。</p><p id="pT21p0227b0812" place="inline">印相二小指
<lb n="0227b09" ed="T"/><note n="0227012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔相〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227012"><lem wit="【大】">相</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>鉤。二無名指向外直豎。二中指<note n="0227013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二頭指〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227013"><lem wit="【大】">二頭指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227b10" ed="T"/>反相叉。二大母<note n="0227014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔指〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227014"><lem wit="【大】">指</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>向外直豎。手掌<note n="0227015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">背合＝相背&M062403;【原】，〔背〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227015"><lem wit="【大】">背合</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">相背</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">合</rdg></app>即
<lb n="0227b11" ed="T"/>是其印。如前所說一一諸法。皆用此印即得
<lb n="0227b12" ed="T"/>成就。今我說根本印。以二手右押左內相
<lb n="0227b13" ed="T"/>叉。豎無<note n="0227016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名＋（指）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227016"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">名指</rdg></app>頭相<note n="0227017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合＋（屈）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227017"><lem wit="【大】">合</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">合屈</rdg></app>。二頭指<note n="0227018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔屈〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227018"><lem wit="【大】">屈</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>如鉤。若迎
<lb n="0227b14" ed="T"/>請時向身招。若<note n="0227019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">撥＝發【甲】</note><app n="0227019"><lem wit="【大】">撥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">發</rdg></app>遣時<note n="0227020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（向）&M062403;＋外【原】</note><app n="0227020"><lem wit="【大】">外</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">向外</rdg></app>撥。念<note n="0227021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">請＝誦&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227021"><lem wit="【大】">請</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">誦</rdg></app>時結印
<lb n="0227b15" ed="T"/>當心誦七遍。<note n="0227022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">印＝即&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227022"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">即</rdg></app>頂上散。然後取念珠專<note n="0227023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">住＝注&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227023"><lem wit="【大】">住</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">注</rdg></app>
<lb n="0227b16" ed="T"/>念誦。</p><p id="pT21p0227b1603" place="inline">次說吉祥天<note n="0227024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">女＋（身）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227024"><lem wit="【大】">女</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">女身</rdg></app>印。<note n="0227025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔以〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227025"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>二手虛心合
<lb n="0227b17" ed="T"/>掌開二頭指二中指二無名指。<note n="0227026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔未〕&M062403;－【原】</note><app n="0227026"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">&lac;</rdg></app>屈如蓮華
<lb n="0227b18" ed="T"/>形。二大指二小指豎合。若念<note n="0227027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">誦＋（時）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0227027"><lem wit="【大】">誦</lem><rdg resp="【原】" wit="【？】">誦時</rdg></app>當心結<note n="0227028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0227028"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0227b19" ed="T"/>誦真言七遍頂上散印。四天王經云。若有人
<lb n="0227b20" ed="T"/>誦念此北方毘沙門天王真言。供養&CB00025;&CB00031;飲
<lb n="0227b21" ed="T"/>食。每月取一十五日二十一日。音聲用單雙
<lb n="0227b22" ed="T"/>絃方響鼓舞。蘇蜜乳粥真心誦念其天王即
<lb n="0227b23" ed="T"/>見其身隨心所願。</p></div1>
<lb n="0227b24" ed="T"/><div1 type="W"><p id="pT21p0227b2401">解穢陀羅尼。</p><p id="pT21p0227b2406" place="inline" type="dharani">唵俱嚕馱唵&CB03928;</p><p id="pT21p0227b2412" place="inline">讚天王頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0227b25" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0227b2501">善利萬物兮惟彼水方　護持國界兮惟我
<lb n="0227b26" ed="T"/>天王　良將受委兮鎮固封彊　精心奉職
<lb n="0227b27" ed="T"/>兮宣託福祥　星宮上勝兮迴架崇岡　靈
<lb n="0227b28" ed="T"/>像儼立兮眾寶嚴莊　威神震曜兮攝伏荒
<lb n="0227b29" ed="T"/>保　又忠貞□兮<note n="0227029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">翅＝翊&M062403;【甲】</note><app n="0227029"><lem wit="【大】">翅</lem><rdg resp="【甲】" wit="【？】">翊</rdg></app>贊聖<note n="0227030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此次行甲本有毘沙門儀軌五字</note>唐</p>
<pb n="0227c" id="T21.1248.0227c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0227c01" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0227c0101"><note n="0227031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">以下甲本無之</note><note n="0227031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>以下甲本無之</note>圓行錄云。北方毘沙門天王隨軍護法真
<lb n="0227c02" ed="T"/>言一卷。不空三藏別行翻譯。八家錄亦爾
<lb n="0227c03" ed="T"/>也。此法請寫於智山慈順僧正染筆。&CB01267;尾
<lb n="0227c04" ed="T"/>山之本。愛染院大宣等對挍之。予亦挍閱
<lb n="0227c05" ed="T"/>以上本。</p>
<lb n="0227c06" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0227c0601">　時享和辛酉八月　　長谷僧快道誌</p>
<lb n="0227c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT21p0227c0701">　一校加筆畢　　　　　　　　慈順</p>
